  "description": "<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 9\"><div class=\"layoutArea\"><div class=\"column\"><p><span style=\"font-family:'CIDFont+F1'\">For your Planetside Settlement, Roll d20 and pick 1-2 entries from the relevant column in the Oracle. A population of \"hundreds\" or more are “Medium-Large”. The results are suggestions for the </span><span style=\"font-family:'CIDFont+F5'\">primary </span><span style=\"font-family:'CIDFont+F1'\">industries in the Settlement.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:'CIDFont+F1'\">When you roll a result of “Manufacturing” on one of the Industries Oracles, roll 1d20 on the Manufacturing Oracle, referencing the relevant column for the Settlement Type.</span></p></div></div></div>",
